What?

01:06:33.221 --> 01:06:35.755
- Well, I mean...
- Don't...

01:06:35.757 --> 01:06:38.391
Don't lie, Anthony.
I know that you're...

01:06:38.393 --> 01:06:40.693
I know you have
a received version

01:06:40.695 --> 01:06:44.697
of who I am supposed to be
at any one time.

01:06:44.699 --> 01:06:46.601
- I don't... That's not...
- But nobody has...

01:06:47.601 --> 01:06:49.637
You know?
I have... (SCOFFS)

