of the task ahead,

01:07:13.427 --> 01:07:15.762
and I think you
just need to relax

01:07:15.764 --> 01:07:18.363
and make sure
you're prepared...

01:07:18.365 --> 01:07:22.501
I am prepared. I am.
This is... This is preparing.

