01:08:02.210 --> 01:08:03.876
I can hopefully...

01:08:03.878 --> 01:08:05.512
Mmm-hmm. Yeah.

01:08:05.514 --> 01:08:07.479
WOMAN: And have
a tighter curl.

01:08:07.481 --> 01:08:09.518
- JULIE: Okay.
