01:08:14.523 --> 01:08:17.756
CREWMAN: This is
sort of all right.

01:08:17.759 --> 01:08:19.261
CAMERAMAN:
No, it's great.

01:08:21.363 --> 01:08:22.761
- Ooh, sorry.
- CAMERAMAN: For fuck's sake.

01:08:22.764 --> 01:08:24.399
Sorry, sorry.

01:08:26.201 --> 01:08:27.834
Just be careful.

01:08:27.836 --> 01:08:30.903
WOMAN: It's okay
for a few more takes.

01:08:30.904 --> 01:08:33.639
JULIE: Yeah, yeah,
we only need another,

01:08:33.640 --> 01:08:35.274
I mean,
another one or two takes.

