Do you think? How many takes
do you think we'll do?

01:08:39.680 --> 01:08:41.346
CAMERAMAN: Well, how long
is a piece of string?

01:08:41.349 --> 01:08:42.648
We shoot till
we've got it, right?

01:08:42.649 --> 01:08:44.349
Okay, yeah.

01:08:44.350 --> 01:08:46.185
But we will need to reset
if that's the case.

01:08:46.188 --> 01:08:49.188
Yeah, okay, we'll make sure
that it's... It will stay.

01:08:49.189 --> 01:08:50.626
- Yeah.
- You know.

01:08:52.225 --> 01:08:53.528
Are you all right?

01:08:55.895 --> 01:08:57.899
No, I just,
I just, um...

01:08:58.765 --> 01:09:00.469
I'm just longing
to be home.

01:09:01.935 --> 01:09:03.439
Mmm.

01:09:11.947 --> 01:09:13.515
Do you want me
to come back?

01:09:22.591 --> 01:09:25.294
Okay. Well,
I'll see you later.

01:09:26.828 --> 01:09:28.264
Okay, bye-bye.

